msg: Big move of all the security.spi interface from the jetspeed-api into the security component.
These interfaces have no purpose in the public api and can only be used within the context of the security component itself.
Furthermore, and the primary reason, keeping them in the public api would break the implementation shielding, especially with regards to the new JetspeedPermission implementation
